---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Piyush Mehta"
  description="Learn about how your data is collected, used, and protected on piyushmehta.com"
  pageType="website"
>
  <main class="privacy-policy">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
      <header class="mb-12 text-center">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-accent to-accent-light bg-clip-text"
        >
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">Last updated: June 3, 2025</p>
      </header>

      <div class="policy-content space-y-8">
        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            1. Introduction
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            Welcome to piyushmehta.com ("the Website"). This Privacy Policy
            explains how I collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your
            information when you visit my website.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            I respect your privacy and am committed to protecting your personal
            data. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully to understand my
            practices regarding your personal data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            1A. Where We Are Based
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            Piyush Mehta and this website (piyushmehta.com) are based in
            Toronto, Ontario, Canada. All data is processed and managed in
            accordance with Canadian privacy laws and regulations.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            2. Information I Collect
          </h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-text-primary">
            2.1 Personal Information
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            When you visit the Website, I may collect certain information about
            you, such as:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            <li>Name and email address (if provided through contact forms)</li>
            <li>Information you choose to provide in messages</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mb-3 text-text-primary">
            2.2 Log Data and Analytics
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            I collect standard log data and use analytics services that may
            record:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            <li>IP address</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Pages visited and time spent on pages</li>
            <li>Referring website addresses</li>
            <li>Other statistics</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            3. How I Use Your Information
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            I use the information I collect for various purposes, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            <li>Responding to your inquiries and messages</li>
            <li>Improving the Website and user experience</li>
            <li>Understanding how visitors use the Website</li>
            <li>
              Sending you updates or newsletters (only with your explicit
              consent)
            </li>
            <li>Protecting the Website against unauthorized access</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            4. Cookies and Tracking Technologies
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            The Website uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to track
            activity and store certain information. Cookies are files with a
            small amount of data that may include an anonymous unique
            identifier.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            You can instruct your browser to refuse all cookies or to indicate
            when a cookie is being sent. However, if you do not accept cookies,
            you may not be able to use some portions of the Website.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            I use the following types of cookies:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            <li>
              Essential cookies: Necessary for the Website to function properly
            </li>
            <li>
              Analytics cookies: Help me understand how visitors interact with
              the Website
            </li>
            <li>
              Preference cookies: Enable the Website to remember your
              preferences
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            5. Third-Party Services
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            I may use third-party services that collect, monitor, and analyze
            data. These third parties have their own privacy policies addressing
            how they use such information.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">These services may include:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            <li>Google Analytics</li>
            <li>Vercel Analytics</li>
            <li>GitHub (for code hosting and project display)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            6. Data Security
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            The security of your data is important to me, but remember that no
            method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic
            storage is 100% secure. While I strive to use commercially
            acceptable means to protect your personal information, I cannot
            guarantee its absolute security.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            7. Your Data Protection Rights
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding
            your personal data, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            <li>The right to access, update, or delete your information</li>
            <li>The right to rectification (to correct inaccurate data)</li>
            <li>The right to object to processing of your data</li>
            <li>The right to data portability</li>
            <li>The right to withdraw consent</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            If you wish to exercise any of these rights, please contact me using
            the information provided at the end of this Privacy Policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            8. Children's Privacy
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            The Website is not intended for use by children under 13 years of
            age. I do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information
            from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and you are
            aware that your child has provided personal information, please
            contact me so that I can take necessary actions.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            9. Changes to This Privacy Policy
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. I will notify
            you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page
            and updating the "Last updated" date at the top.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any
            changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are
            posted on this page.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            10. Contact Information
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact
            me at:
          </p>
          <div
            class="bg-surface-secondary p-4 rounded-lg border border-card-border"
          >
            <p class="mb-2 text-text-primary font-medium">Piyush Mehta</p>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">Based in Toronto, Ontario, Canada</p>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">
              Email: <a
                href="mailto:me@piyushmehta.com"
                class="text-accent hover:underline">me@piyushmehta.com</a
              >
            </p>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">
              Website: <a
                href="https://piyushmehta.com"
                class="text-accent hover:underline">piyushmehta.com</a
              >
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="policy-section">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text-primary">
            11. Jurisdiction
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4 text-text-secondary">
            This Privacy Policy and any disputes related to it are governed by
            the laws of the Province of Ontario and the federal laws of Canada
            applicable therein. You agree to submit to the exclusive
            jurisdiction of the courts in Toronto, Ontario, Canada.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    .privacy-policy {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 4rem);
    }

    .policy-section {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      background-color: rgba(var(--color-bg-rgb), 0.5);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .policy-section {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
    }

    .policy-section:hover {
      border-color: var(--color-accent);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(var(--color-accent-rgb), 0.1);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
